From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:28:43 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: cix: Add Sky1 SoC infrastructure drivers

Add core SoC support for CIX Sky1 including:
- SoC info, bus performance monitor, DDR low-power driver
- ACPI resource lookup and scan handlers (GPU, USB)
- Sky1 PDC wake interrupt controller
- GIC-v3 errata workaround for Sky1
- Sky1 nvmem and hwspinlock drivers
- syscon ACPI platform driver support
- arch_topology CPC/CPPC performance scale helpers
